Welcome to the source distribution of the Lethe Private Messaging system.

Overview
========

Lethe is an HTML5 web application, designed to allow two or more parties to communicate securely and easily without the use of web browser plugins or non-standard technologies.  Lethe provides strong cryptography between 


Build Instructions
==================

Erlang Backend
--------------

Software Requirements:
    * GNU Make
    * Erlang/OTS R14b or later
    * Yaws 1.88

To build the Erlang backend, cd into the erlang directory and issue make:

> make

An Erlang distribution archive (ZIP format) will be created in the erlang directory.

Javascript Frontend
-------------------

Software requirements:
    * Apple Dashcode (part of XCode)
